{"tid":703951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手提風扇充電爆炸震毀窗","createTime":"2018-06-16T05:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T16:01:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"618a974e1dd175441c3c76343ab8b2747de186a4","tid":703951,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180616/20422102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180616%2F20422102&d=bTxF3GTHIY4ejja7HVfaof7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a5c12874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180616%2F20422102&h=47aff8b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180616/20422102</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月16日 <br />\n<br />\n手提風扇充電爆炸震毀窗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180616/large/a1805a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180616%2Flarge%2Fa1805a.gif&h=7e3bfe0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人夏天常用的手提風扇，在台灣卻接連發生爆炸事故。台灣苗栗鄒姓男子昨在facebook稱，他買入的一款中國製鋰電手提風扇（左圖），在充電時爆炸（右圖），連窗戶都被震毀，直言：「若是炸在小朋友手上&hellip;&hellip;後果不堪設想！」在本月1日，台灣一名媽媽也發帖稱，其子因使用大陸製小風扇的鋰電池爆炸，導致手指二級燙傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鋰電中國製造<br />\n<br />\n據悉，鄒男所買的RONEVER手提風扇是中國製造。台灣《蘋果》向RONEVER手提風扇的台灣進口商，向聯科技公司陳姓業務經理求證，他表示該產品推出3年多來，從未有過類似事件，電扇使用的「18650鋰電池」，通過合格認證。他懷疑電池出問題的可能性較高，已與鄒男和解，賠償對方新貨。他表示已通知出售該款手提風扇的網絡商，將該批號產品下架，回收檢測。<br />\n<br />\n此外，台灣網民陳女士本月1日亦稱，其子當日在學校聽說同學帶回來的手提式小風扇充電有問題，他接過檢查發現很燙，打開電池蓋散熱時，電池變紅爆炸，導致其手指二級燙傷。涉事小風扇為台灣逸盛科技公司Esense手提式USB風扇，也是在中國製造。有專家指，使用USB充電的手提風扇，若懷疑電池質量差，應避免過度充電。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n南台灣暴雨　高雄13,500戶一度停電<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n年賺3億網紅捲情色醜聞　 會計仔虧空千萬打賞"},{"pid":"3899145f9de1ac9bc6f78547d5198148a082ebff","tid":703951,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0776642fe876aba878e0f4aa7ca610bc6086d7c8","tid":703951,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3899145f9de1ac9bc6f78547d5198148a082ebff","tid":703951,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"咩牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358b8b8a77d4b9a4f7888565fb9e5987ec114f6b","tid":703951,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"共田係最好<br />\n雖然一樣支那，但係芭蕉扇係佢出先"},{"pid":"a065e39b4b63fd880d6fd9907fde2a5140d6440a","tid":703951,"uid":35716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:23:53.000Z","msg":"多數都係電池出事<br />\n好多舖頭為了減底成平本，會自行換上雜牌低容量18650電池.....<br />\n<br />\n因為平十元八塊會好賣好多...."},{"pid":"039fdfcd32ed6645126a8214c13b1a91feb972fd","tid":703951,"uid":27133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3899145f9de1ac9bc6f78547d5198148a082ebff","tid":703951,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"咩牌"},{"pid":"86f90eafbfac8984279b728fd66f09c74c217056","tid":703951,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"有把共田用左幾年都無事"},{"pid":"ef71152b47b61fa91caeb6792eebb7f4c0c902c3","tid":703951,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T16:01:54.000Z","msg":"成蟲：中蟈的會爆炸.jpg"}]}